{"tid":140854,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"召集失緊業既 IT 巴打","createTime":"2017-03-02T13:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T07:04:26.000Z","uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d95ffb7692393d65e2d3b12f36aa2830c5bfd52e","tid":140854,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"IT 業正直發展逢勃, 在 IT 業龍頭美國既強勢帶領下日益壯大<br />\nAI, IoT, VR/AR, AppDev 等等範疇在過去幾年都獲得鉅額投資, 而且有增無減<br />\n因此在唔少發逹國家催生左一大堆以科技同研發為主既 start up 公司, 包括香港<br />\n但呢啲公司成立之初大概都會遇到一個共同問題: 請唔到人!<br />\n所以, 係 IT 人才成為全球最搶手員工既 2017 年, 作為 IT 人既你重要為搵份好工而煩腦既話, 豈有此理 !?<br />\n如果真係咁既話, 唔緊要, 加入呢個 TG group, 大量好工等緊你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAzqz5w8E9j5O8MNMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAAzqz5w8E9j5O8MNMA&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2b817303\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAAzqz5w8E9j5O8MNMA</a><br />\n<br />\nFor the benefits of all Hackers, Programmers and Mathematicians !"},{"pid":"cf71c76be5608d3554a2b6ef6eac6e02d3a8e0ca","tid":140854,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"sor, 轉左link <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEDkRLjfB4mh6WhOIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEDkRLjfB4mh6WhOIw&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHaf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8bc7c7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEDkRLjfB4mh6WhOIw</a>"},{"pid":"662b04577f019ada9b99d664951f2590e3c9dade","tid":140854,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"不如整個<strong>資技搵工app</strong>好過啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebefc1d43e1217d71dfb44a05d34739ce80b457","tid":140854,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如整個<strong>資技搵工app</strong>好過啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm